Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
content-type: application/json

{

  "name":        "Laura",
  "type":        "owner",
  "email":       "lauraa@gmail.com",
  "password":    "B@tatinha123",
  "phone":       "19844453838"

}

### editanto apenas um campo de usuario.
PUT https://voyagegabi.onrender.com/user/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
content-type: application/json

{

  "name":        "Kevingay",
